select count(poi_id) as tot_properties from (
             select poi_id
             from spectrum_db.pre_166_properties_contents_daily_count pcdc
             where content_date >= date '2020-12-15'
             AND content_date <= date '2021-06-15'
             AND date_partition >= DATE_TRUNC('month', date '2020-12-15')
             AND date_partition <= DATE_TRUNC('month', date '2021-06-15')
              AND country = 'italy' AND county = 'l''aquila' AND state = 'abruzzo'    AND content_type IN ('review', 'taggedpost')
             group by poi_id
) properties

SELECT DATE_TRUNC('day', r.checkindate) as period,
       COALESCE(SUM(r.maxavailablerooms),0) AS total_offers
FROM spectrum_db.rates_saturation_v3 r
         INNER JOIN  spectrum_db.poi_urls pu ON pu.url_id = r.urlid
WHERE   r.checkindate >= DATE_TRUNC('day', date '2021-03-17')  AND
        r.checkindate <= DATE_TRUNC('day',date '2021-09-13')   AND
        r.date_partition >= date_trunc('month', DATE_TRUNC('day', date '2021-03-17')) AND
        r.date_partition <= date_trunc('month', DATE_TRUNC('day',date '2021-09-13'))
        AND country = 'italy' AND county = 'pordenone' AND state = 'friuli-venezia giulia'
        AND is_sample = true AND class = '4'
        
        AND r.numberofguests = 2
group by DATE_TRUNC('day', r.checkindate)
order by period

SELECT sum(contents_positive)                                        as pos,
       sum(contents_negative)                                        as neg,
       sum(contents_neutral)                                         as neu,
       sum(contents_positive + contents_negative + contents_neutral) as tot,
        entity_type AS group_type
FROM spectrum_db.pre_166_properties_contents_daily_count
WHERE content_date >= date '2020-11-01'
  AND content_date <= date '2021-05-31'
  AND date_partition >= DATE_TRUNC('month', date '2020-11-01')
  AND date_partition <= DATE_TRUNC('month', date '2021-05-31')
  AND country = 'italy' AND county = 'l''aquila' AND state = 'abruzzo'     AND content_type IN ('review', 'taggedpost')
  AND  entity_type is not null
  GROUP BY entity_type
ORDER BY tot desc
